OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1772971376
OL,3,CLiberal Democrats reveal childcare
OL,4,Cpledge ahead of Senedd Election
OL,6,FThe Welsh Liberal Democrat leader Jane
OL,7,FDodds has said "people deserve honesty
OL,8,Fin politics" as she announced a number
OL,9,Fof promises at her party's conference
OL,10,Fin Cardiff.
OL,12,FThey've promised 30 hours of free
OL,13,Fchildcare from the age of nine months
OL,14,Fto four years, if they were to win the
OL,15,FSenedd Election.
OL,17,FPlaid Cymru have also made a promise
OL,18,Fon childcare- offering 20 hours for
OL,19,Fall 2 year olds and moves to tackle
OL,20,Fchild poverty including piloting a
OL,21,FWelsh Child Payment known as Cynnal.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
