OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1772971376
OL,3,CLiberal Democrats reveal childcare
OL,4,Cpledge ahead of Senedd Election
OL,6,FOn health, Jane Dodds said 'there is
OL,7,Fpressure before people ever reach the
OL,8,Fhospital door. The pressures of daily
OL,9,Flife, of housing, of stress, of mental
OL,10,Fhealth, of people trying to keep
OL,11,Feverything together.
OL,13,F"And there is pressure after hospital
OL,14,Ftoo. When someone is ready to leave
OL,15,Fbut cannot go home because the care
OL,16,Fthey need simply is not there.
OL,18,F"Fixing social care is how we save our
OL,19,FNHS"
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
