CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1772971376
OL,3,CLiberal Democrats reveal childcare
OL,4,Cpledge ahead of Senedd Election
OL,6,FShe promised to create thousands of
OL,7,Fnew social care places and at-home
OL,8,Fsupport, and train more GPs, as well
OL,9,Fdelivering a "world-class" mental
OL,10,Fhealth service.
OL,12,FThey say if they cannot find the money
OL,13,Ffor this in the Senedd budget, then
OL,14,Fthey are prepared to ask for an extra
OL,15,Fpenny on income tax to fund social
OL,16,Fcare, saying "fixing this will cost
OL,17,Fmoney. There is no serious answer that
OL,18,Fpretends otherwise.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
