PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1772971376
OL,3,CLiberal Democrats reveal childcare
OL,4,Cpledge ahead of Senedd Election
OL,6,F"People deserve honesty in politics.
OL,7,FThey know when they are being offered
OL,8,Fa fantasy. They know when someone is
OL,9,Fsaying whatever it takes for a whiff
OL,10,Fof power."
OL,12,FThe Liberal Democrats are currently
OL,13,Fsixth in the polls, at 5%, while Welsh
OL,14,FNationalist party Plaid Cymru lead.
OL,16,FThe Lib Dems are pledging to "make
OL,17,Fsure not a single penny of Welsh
OL,18,FGovernment money is wasted on the
OL,19,Findependence agenda."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
