OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1772971376
OL,3,CLiberal Democrats reveal childcare
OL,4,Cpledge ahead of Senedd Election
OL,6,FThe party says instead the money "will
OL,7,Fgo where people need it. Into our
OL,8,Fhealth service, our communities and
OL,9,Four economy."
OL,11,FThey also say they will review
OL,12,Fbusiness rates, and invest in proper
OL,13,Fbroadband for businesses, as well as
OL,14,Fimprove public transport.
OL,16,FOn agriculture, they're promising to
OL,17,Fdeliver a multi-year settlement for
OL,18,FWelsh farming.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/7
