OL,3,CLiberal Democrats reveal childcare
OL,4,Cpledge ahead of Senedd Election
OL,6,FDelivering her speech in Cardiff, Jane
OL,7,FDodds said "Rebuilding faith in
OL,8,Fpolitics is hard. Restoring public
OL,9,Fservices under this much pressure is
OL,10,Fhard. But while institutions crumble
OL,11,Fthe unyielding spirit of Wales is as
OL,12,Falive as ever.
OL,14,F"Through love of each other and love
OL,15,Ffor our communities, Wales can start a
OL,16,Fnew chapter, if only government allows
OL,17,Fit to do so
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/7
